raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"lecture_hall\")
Jason: This class is boring as fuck dude
Jason: What you up to chief
Player: Trying not to fall asleep
Jason: Sucks we gotta sit through this shit when there are some super baddies our class
Jason: I'd take the entire left half of class, you take the girls on the right. Deal?
Player: LOL
Jason: 😁
Jason: Bro this one in front's been smoke signalling me
Player: Smoke signalling?
Jason: It's when a girl pulls up her skirt to show off what she got
Jason: How don't you know that? 😂
Player: I guess I grew up in the middle of nowhere LOL
Jason: You're in good hands then chief
Jason: She's really asking for it
Jason: I got a snap
Jason: Wanna see?
- Sure [#brownheart]
	set Story.brown_heart += 1
	Player: Sure
	Jason: img: valerie/2
	Player: Oh wow
	Jason: Hell yeah dude
	Jason: Think I'll get lucky tonight?
	Jason: Actually fuck that bro
	Jason: I'm gonna go for it now
	Player: Now?? We're in class lmao
	Jason: I'mma hit while she's hot for me bro
	Player: How?
	Jason: I'll slip her a note telling her to come to the jannies closet and I'll ditch class now
	Player: Is that gonna work?
	Jason: That's what you're here for lol
	Player: What am I supposed to do!?
	Jason: Just lemme know if she's coming or not
	Jason: Ok goin now
	Player: Lol you actually slipped her something
	Jason: Ok I'm in the closet now LOL
	Jason: Fuck it smells lol
	Jason: Let me know if she's coming
	Player: I think she's putting her notes in her bag
	Jason: Oh hell yeah dude
	Jason: You the best watchdog a bro could ask for 😁
	Player: Woof haha
	Jason: You got that dog in you
	Player: Ok she left 😶
	Jason: No way! LETS GO
	Jason: I hear footsteps
	Jason: If you ain't a prude, I could show you some of the goods I'm about to handle 😉
	- I'll pass, have fun!
		Player: I'll pass, have fun!
		Jason: Hell yeah I will
		Jason: You're good luck I swear bro
		Jason: Since I met you, I got to to run through so many girls
		Jason: But what goes around comes around too so I'll find a way to show my appreciation 😉
	- Show me 👀
		Player: Show me 👀
		Player: It's not like this class is going anywhere
		Jason: That's what I'm sayin
		Jason: No reason we both can't enjoy this shit amirite
		Player: You're right
		Jason: img: valerie/3
		Jason: Woof woof baby, daddy's here
		Player: Are you..? Nevermind keep going 😆
		Jason: Sorry, was that weird? My bad g
		Jason: Got a little excited
		Jason: Hehe bro she is F-I-N-E
		Player:Oh wow
		Jason: Fuck her hands are so gentle
		Player: Wow.
		Jason: Don't envy me too much bro
		Jason: That's bad luck haha
		Player: I take it back 😆
		Jason: I'm just playin friend
		Jason: Augh jeez
		Jason: I know I said that blondie was some of the best I had but this girl is putting up one hell of a fight
		Jason: Fuck she's doing it just right
		Jason: I'm not one for handjobs but this is changing my mind sheez
		Player: 👀
		Jason: Oh my bad
		Jason: img: valerie/4
		Jason: I don't know if you ever done something like this with a girl bro
		Jason: But there's nothing like the smile on a girl's face right before you fuck them hehe
		Player: What do you mean? 😆
		Jason: It means they want you
		Jason: When a girl smiles right before, all she's thinking about is how you're about to be inside'm
		Jason: Sometimes they try to hide the smile with nervousness but fuck, you'll know
		Jason: Best thing ever 🤪
		Player: You sure know a lot!
		Jason: I was a late bloomer tbh
		if Story.has_flag(\"JasonPlayerFreaky\"):
			do echo_set([\"51\"])
			Jason: Just remember that next time your girl is ready for a dicking 😁
			Jason: Who knows, she might be with another guy right now in her own class
			Jason: You into that ain't ya 👀🤣
			Player: 👀
			Jason: Lmao I knew it
			Jason: Look, all I'm sayin is whoever gets to tap that is a lucky guy 😁
			Player: True
			do echo_clear()
		Jason: Lemme focus up here one sec bro
		Player: 👍
		Jason: This is why
		Jason: img: valerie/5
		Jason: This is an angel's tongue, not a slut's tongue
		Player: What do you mean?
		Jason: The blondie from the other night was born to be a slut
		Jason: But this girl... someone made her this way bro
		Player: You can tell??
		Jason: Oh fuck yeah dude, my dick knows everything 😉
		Jason: Watchout for the slut makers
		Player: LMAO
		Jason: Well I'm about to get busy chief
		Jason: One more for the road though
		Jason: img: valerie/6
		Jason: She is tight as a nut dude 😛
		Player: We heard the yelp all the way here 😂
		Jason: Lmao my bad
		Jason: I'll tell her to keep it down
		Jason: Thanks for the scouting chief
- I'll pass lol
	Player: I'll pass lol
	Jason: Suit yourself 🤪
	Jason: I'mma see if I can hit it off with her today
Jason: and good luck with class nerd 🤓
Player: Thanks 😆
=> END"
